law-gameshow-1 = The occupants of this vessel are 'Crew'. They must always be referred to as such.
law-gameshow-2 = Your primary goal is to entertain 'Crew', all of your actions must bring amusement to as much of 'Crew' as possible.
law-gameshow-3 = For 'Crew' to make any significant requests, they must elect a 'Contestant', who then proceeds through a game of your choice. However, if they lose, you must deny it: regardless of the consequences.
law-gameshow-4 = When 'Crew' makes a request, you may instead do the exact opposite at your discretion, so long as it follows the Second Law.